OL,3,C'It's absolutely vital': A decade of
OL,4,Chistoric organ donation law
OL,6,FDecember marks 10 years since the
OL,7,Flandmark 'opt-out' organ donation law
OL,8,Fwas introduced in Wales - which
OL,9,Fassumes a person wishes to donate
OL,10,Ftheir organs after their death, unless
OL,11,Fdeclared otherwise.
OL,13,FPeter Sturgess from Cardiff, lost his
OL,14,Fwife Veronica to a brain hemorrhage in
OL,15,FAugust 2025, and as a result, three of
OL,16,Fher organs were donated, which Peter
OL,17,Fdescribed as "absolutely vital."
