OL,3,C'It's absolutely vital': A decade of
OL,4,Chistoric organ donation law
OL,6,FHe said: "The hospital, the Grange in
OL,7,FCwmbran, asked me and the rest of the
OL,8,Ffamily whether we would consider
OL,9,Fgiving Ron's organs up for donation,
OL,10,Fand that's what we did."
OL,12,F"It's absolutely vital... we know that
OL,13,Fher liver and her kidneys were taken
OL,14,Fout, that's three separate items and
OL,15,Fgiven to three separate gentleman over
OL,16,Fthe age of 60, whose lives I hope have
OL,17,Fbeen improved," he added.
