OL,3,C'It's absolutely vital': A decade of
OL,4,Chistoric organ donation law
OL,6,F"Knowing that there is a little bit of
OL,7,FRonnie out there living, that's also a
OL,8,Fcomfort... I'm really, really glad
OL,9,Fthat we donated her organs and that
OL,10,Fthree people's lives have been
OL,11,Fimproved."
OL,13,FAs part of the legislation, families
OL,14,Fwill always be consulted about organ
OL,15,Fdonation.
OL,17,FSince the law came into force on 1
OL,18,FDecember 2015, 640 organs have been
OL,19,Fdonated via deemed consent - from 198
OL,20,Fdeceased donors.
