OL,3,C'It's absolutely vital': A decade of
OL,4,Chistoric organ donation law
OL,6,FBut, Wales still has the highest
OL,7,Fproportion of opt out registrations at
OL,8,F5.8% compared to England and Scotland
OL,9,Fat 4.0% and 3.4% respectively.
OL,11,FThe Chief Medical Officer for Wales,
OL,12,FIsabel Oliver, described the
OL,13,Flegislation as "wonderful", but
OL,14,Fstressed the importance of registering
OL,15,Fyour organ donation decision, to
OL,16,Fprovide families with certainty around
OL,17,Fyour choice.
