OL,3,C'It's absolutely vital': A decade of
OL,4,Chistoric organ donation law
OL,6,FShe said: "As part of the legislation
OL,7,Fwe do ask families for their support
OL,8,Ffor transplantation, we know when we
OL,9,Fregister our consent to donate which
OL,10,Fwe can do online... We are then able
OL,11,Fto proceed with donation in about 90%
OL,12,Fof cases.
OL,14,F"Through the deemed consent
OL,15,Flegislation when we ask families, it's
OL,16,Fabout 50 - 60%, so this is why it's so
OL,17,Fimportant that we register our
OL,18,Fintentions."
