OL,3,C'It's absolutely vital': A decade of
OL,4,Chistoric organ donation law
OL,6,FThe latest statistics show that the
OL,7,Fpercentage of the population of Wales
OL,8,Fwho have officially registered to 'opt-
OL,9,Fin' is at 43.9%.
OL,11,FDespite deemed consent now being the
OL,12,Fsystem for the whole of the UK,
OL,13,FAnthony Clarkson, the Director of
OL,14,FOrgan Donation and Transplant at NHS
OL,15,FBlood and Transplant said the
OL,16,Flegislation "is not a silver bullet."
OL,18,F"It is an important piece of the
OL,19,Fjigsaw to improving organ donation,
OL,20,Ftransplant, and consent rates," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
