OL,3,C'It's absolutely vital': A decade of
OL,4,Chistoric organ donation law
OL,6,F"I would urge everyone in Wales who
OL,7,Fsupports organ donation to register
OL,8,Ftheir decision and make it clear that
OL,9,Fit's what you want should the worst
OL,10,Fhappen.
OL,12,F"It only takes two minutes to
OL,13,Fregister, but it could save the lives
OL,14,Fof people who so desperately need a
OL,15,Ftransplant."
